videos.description: LeVante Bellamy breaks through the hole and jets down the sideline for a 66-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Long TD gives Western Michigan early lead

videos.description: Buffalo's Drew Anderson connects with a wide open Kamathi Holsey for a would-be touchdown, but Sam Beal runs him down and forces the fumble.
videos.headline: Wide open TD turns into 53-yard fumble recovery

videos.description: Drew Anderson finds Jacob Martinez wide open down the middle who jogs in for the 64-yard score.
videos.headline: Buffalo capitalizes on blown coverage for TD pass

videos.description: Emmanuel Reed dives in the pile for a rushing touchdown to finish off a long Buffalo drive.
videos.headline: Bulls take the lead on short TD run

videos.description: Jon Wassink sends it to D'Wayne Eskridge, who is wide open on the sideline and he walks in to the end zone.
videos.headline: Broncos take the lead on second long TD pass

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin takes the screen pass and follows his blockers to stroll into the end zone from 20 yards out.
videos.headline: Screen pass leads to easy TD for the Broncos

videos.description: Drew Anderson hits Anthony Johnson with a laser throw for his second touchdown pass of the day.
videos.headline: Passing TD brings the Bulls within 3

videos.description: Drew Anderson links up with K.J. Osborn down the sideline who finishes the job and scores to take the lead.
videos.headline: Anderson throws 3rd TD pass of the afternoon

videos.description: Jon Wassink finds Donnie Ernsberger in the back of the end zone to regain the lead for the Broncos.
videos.headline: Wassink notches his 3rd TD pass and eclipses 200 yards

videos.description: Drew Anderson connects with Kamathi Holsey in the corner for the 5-yard score in overtime.
videos.headline: Buffalo with first OT TD

videos.description: Jon Wassink lobs it into the end zone and Donnie Ernsberger comes down with the grab for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Broncos answer in OT with passing TD

videos.description: Broncos pull off the double pass from Keishawn Watson to Jon Wassink and score in double overtime.
videos.headline: Double pass from Broncos takes the lead in 2nd OT

videos.description: Drew Anderson throws a perfect ball to Anthony Johnson for the 25-yard touchdown that sends it to the third overtime.
videos.headline: Bulls answer with dime TD pass from Anderson

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin rushes in the touchdown to take the lead and then some trickery leads to the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Broncos take lead in 4 OT with TD and 2 pt. conversion

videos.description: Drew Anderson passes to K.J. Osborn for the touchdown and then Anderson catches the double reverse for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Buffalo sends game to 5th OT  with TD and 2 pt. conversion

videos.description: Western Michigan's Donnie Ernsberger scores a 14-yard touchdown in overtime, and his sister runs into the end zone to join in on the celebration. She's asked to leave the stadium soon after as the game hadn't concluded.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sister celebrates brother's touchdown on field during game) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sister celebrates brother's touchdown on field during game

videos.description: Drew Anderson makes a great pass for the touchdown in the 5th overtime, but the two point conversion failed when the Broncos defense ripped the ball out after the catch.
videos.headline: Bulls score great TD but can't hang on for 2pt. conversion

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin scores the touchdown to tie it at 59, but the two-point conversion was stopped short, sending it to a 6th overtime.
videos.headline: Broncos score TD in 5th OT but fail 2pt. conversion

videos.description: Jon Wassink passes to Watson for the score in the 6th overtime, but he gets stopped when he scrambles for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Broncos pass for TD in 6th OT, fail 2 pt. conversion

videos.description: Drew Anderson scrambles for the touchdown, but is stopped just shy of the goal line for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Bulls match Broncos with TD and failed 2 pt. conversion in 6th OT

videos.description: Jarvion Franklin keeps his legs moving and scores the game winning touchdown for the Broncos.
videos.headline: Broncos win in 7th OT
